description:
Share anything to your computer

Description

Easiest and fastest way to share text, images or any files from your phone to your computer or phones.

Feature

- Share to your computer, use browser to download the files shared (require no installation on computer) - Share to other phones, choose "scan QR code" - Through wifi no internet access required - No ads, free - Open source check the full source code at https://github.com/jimmod/ShareToComputer
